that she is incredible.

14:25.400 --> 14:26.980
All right,
just do me a favor.

14:26.980 --> 14:28.980
Stop talking about me.

14:28.980 --> 14:30.990
My ears can't take it
any longer.

14:33.490 --> 14:34.490
