Yeah, right, Fonz.

16:20.150 --> 16:21.730
Rich, I've got to talk
to you about something.

16:21.730 --> 16:23.230
You'll go later.

16:23.230 --> 16:25.730
Maybe we should
play something she
can keep up with.

16:25.730 --> 16:27.240
Yeah.
Yeah.

