Uh, how about
"Clementine"?

16:30.360 --> 16:32.440
"Clementine"?
Yeah.

16:32.440 --> 16:33.940
Oh, don't you know
anything more hip?

16:33.940 --> 16:35.410
How about uh,
"Splish Splash"?

16:35.780 --> 16:39.370
Do we know
"Splish Splash"?

